These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-1::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, horse, ferret
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the owner of the ferret##7
3. the owner of the horse is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1    |  2   |   3   |  4   |
| Pet   | horse | chinchilla | ferret | hedgehog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, cucumber, pepper, cabbage
1. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person eating pepper is somewhere between the person eating cucumber and the person eating carrot##7
3. the person eating pepper is between the person eating cucumber and the person eating cabbage##2

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food   | carrot | cabbage | pepper | cucumber |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-3::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, apple, apricot, strawberry
1. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating apple##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person eating apple##7
3. the person eating apricot is somewhere to the right of the person eating strawberry##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |  2   |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | tomato | apple | strawberry | apricot |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, roller, quad-bike, trike
1. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the roller##7
2. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5
3. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the trike and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |   3   |    4    |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship | trike | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, satire, mystery, drama
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
2. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching drama movies##2
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the left or right of the person watching mystery movies##3
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person watching drama movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |   3   |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | superhero | satire | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, brazilian, japanese, polish
1. the spanish is somewhere between the polish and the brazilian##7
2. the japanese is somewhere between the spanish and the polish##7
3. the japanese is on the left or right of the polish##3
4. the japanese is somewhere to the right of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |     3     |    4    |
| Nationality   | polish | japanese | spanish | brazilian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, coffee, sprite
1. the person drinking sprite is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking juice##7
2. the person drinking coffee is somewhere between the person drinking sprite and the person drinking soy-milk##7
3. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |    2     |   3   |      4      |
| Beverage   | juice | sprite | coffee | soy-milk |

