3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
4. the person driving the ship is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the roller##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Transport   | roller | airplane | ship | quad-bike |

